How did you and Petal meet?

23
00:01:46,390 --> 00:01:47,910
- I... 
 - I'm her tutor.

24
00:01:47,910 --> 00:01:49,520
I help her with schoolwork.

25
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:52,080
So you're agreeing to tutor me?

26
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:55,900
Yes. Go to the Jinghai University.

27
00:01:55,910 --> 00:02:00,660
Great! Then, just take these. Here.

28
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:01,600
What is this?

29
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,910
Isn't it written on there?

30
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:05,130
This is ginseng. And this, too.

31
00:02:05,130 --> 00:02:07,060
And these are cordyceps.

32
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:08,320
They're all for you.

33
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:11,360
Since you've agreed to tutor me, I have to show my gratitude.

34
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,870
Please accept these.

35
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,120
Take good care of your health.

36
00:02:27,928 --> 00:02:29,360
   

37
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,040
   

38
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:41,060
How about I make you some ginseng tea first?

39
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:43,020
Senior Brother Lin.

40
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:47,910
She’s just someone from my high school who’s a few years younger than me.

41
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:50,140
Okay, okay, I get it.

42
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:56,150
But I think you really do need to take care of your health.

43
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:58,470
You've been so busy lately, you look worn out.

44
00:02:58,470 --> 00:03:00,460
I can't bear to watch anymore.

45
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:05,610
Just get to the point. Skip the preamble.

46
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:08,460
I'll be direct then.

47
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:12,750
Your parents are coming back for the shareholder meeting.

48
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:16,570
You have to give them a warm welcome.

49
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:22,520
When they come back, Lin Qi should welcome them.

50
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,030
Why should I?

51
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:27,350
We'll greet them at the office. But at home, it's your job.

52
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:31,060
You've been living alone for years now.

53
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:32,710
Aren't you lonely?

54
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:37,520
Once Uncle and Aunt return, this house will be immediately full of life.

55
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:41,130
The spare key's by the door. Don't forget to grab it.

56
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:42,780
And once the date's set, tell me.

57
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:45,340
Okay. I'll find someone to come and clean up a bit.

58
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:47,330
And get the house ready for them.

59
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:51,750
When they get back, I'll just go and stay in my dorm for a few days.

60
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,510
I'm going to sleep.

61
00:04:07,130 --> 00:04:09,390
Why isn't Jiao Jiao up yet?

62
00:04:09,390 --> 00:04:12,470
She's been studying very hard recently. She's too tired.

63
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:15,050
Uncle Zhou gave us some supplements last time.

64
00:04:15,050 --> 00:04:16,410
Check the date on them.

65
00:04:16,410 --> 00:04:18,050
Give the fresh ones to Jiao Jiao.

66
00:04:18,050 --> 00:04:19,220
And give the almost-expired ones to me.

67
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:21,880
You wish. We have to give those to our son.

68
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:24,130
Give me the expired ones then.

69
00:04:26,590 --> 00:04:28,670
Dad, I'm still a kid.

70
00:04:28,670 --> 00:04:30,590
Too many tonics will fry my brain.

71
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:33,180
I have to get to school early for a college exam prep rally today.

72
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:34,690
I can't talk right now. I have to go.

73
00:04:34,690 --> 00:04:36,090
Okay.

74
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,760
Hello, students. 
    

75
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:41,640
 Hello, Principal! 

76
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:46,200
During freshman year, everyone can be carefree.

77
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:49,180
And during sophomore year, you can still laugh and be joyful.

78
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,520
But not during senior year.

79
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,680
Because now is the time to grind.

80
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,810
It's time to work hard.

81
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:02,640
Now, I want you all to ask yourselves,

82
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:05,050
do you know the Memorial Regarding the Northern Expedition, inside and out?

83
00:05:05,050 --> 00:05:07,960
 - No.  
 - Who said no?

84
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,780
Why isn't he here yet?

85
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,790
Where is our class president?

86
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:14,910
Maybe he fell in the toilet.

87
00:05:14,910 --> 00:05:18,790
I think he probably freaked out about going on stage.

88
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:19,960
 Understood. 

89
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,910
Come on, you know him.

90
00:05:21,910 --> 00:05:23,240
Considering his personality,

91
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:26,030
he'll never miss a chance to shine in front of the whole grade.

92
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:29,370
Even if he has to crawl, he'll get himself here.

93
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:31,350
Be careful with your phone.

94
00:05:31,350 --> 00:05:33,200
- It's okay. 
 - The principal is watching.

95
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:36,000
Romain Rolland once said,

96
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:39,350
there's only one true heroism in the world.

97
00:05:39,350 --> 00:05:43,030
It is to see the world as it is, and to love it.

98
00:05:43,030 --> 00:05:45,790
I hope you can see studying as it is

99
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,320
and love it

100
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,560
in order to reach one goal. 
    

101
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,160
Acing the college entrance exam! 
    

102
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,400
So, everyone,

103
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,230
the road is long and arduous,

104
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,980
but the best is yet to come.

105
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:58,420
That's enough with the small talk.

106
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:03,620
Now, let's welcome our student representative to the stage.

107
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,450
   

108
00:06:14,450 --> 00:06:17,180
Dear teachers, fellow students, hello.

109
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:20,620
 - Where are you?  
 - I'm Zhou Shiyun, the class representative from Senior Year, Class 1.

110
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:24,020
 I'm at the entrance. 

111
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:34,950
Crawl... I'll crawl if I have to.

112
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:45,360
Thank you, everyone.

113
